+## Burst-hold awareness lane
+
+The bootstrap now includes a second pulse lane for on-screen awareness messages.
+
+### New pulse-managed UI controls
+- `HoldMajorBurstIntoWalls`
+- `HoldMajorBurstEnemyHP`
+- `PulseExplainBurstHolds`
+- `PulseBurstHoldMessageThrottle`
+
+### New helper behavior
+- Detect broad enemy immunity or wall windows
+- Hold major burst cooldowns during those windows
+- Show a Makulu awareness message explaining why burst is being held
+- Throttle repeated messages so they do not spam
+
+### Example pulse
+```bash
+python PulseSystem/scripts/process_pulse.py PulseSystem/samples/002_explain_major_burst_holds.json
+```
